[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Anonymous entry (sponsor recruitment channel,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      ClinicalTrials.gov landing page, social-media ad)    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver or family-member entry with appropriate    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      authorization                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Vulnerable-populations-aware identity classification]  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Adult self-decision (baseline)                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Parent or guardian for pediatric participant         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (assent and parental permission per 45 CFR 46       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      Subpart D)                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Surrogate decision maker for cognitively impaired    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      adult                                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Protected-population flags (pregnant patients under  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      Subpart B, prisoners under Subpart C, children       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      under Subpart D, older adults, patients with         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      disabilities)                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Per-conversation trial binding]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bind trial_id at session start                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Switching trials within a session triggers a new     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation with new disclosures and new consent    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      posture                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-trial recommendation is structurally           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      prohibited at the tool-dispatcher level              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: verified identity, population posture,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    bound trial_id]                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── TRIAL-CONTEXT LOADING + AMENDMENT TRACKING ────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Per-trial IRB-approved content corpus]                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Protocol summary in IRB-approved language            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Eligibility criteria in IRB-approved language        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recruitment-FAQ entries in IRB-approved language      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Visit-schedule summary                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Study-procedure summary                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sponsor-and-investigator information                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - IRB and protocol identifiers                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Institutional contact information                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Trial-state verification]                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Check trial enrollment status (open, paused, closed) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Check site-specific enrollment status                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Route to alternative pathway if trial is not open    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [IRB-amendment-application mid-conversation handling]   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Snapshot trial-context-version at conversation start │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - On every turn, re-fetch trial-state and compare      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      versions                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - If material amendment detected: branch to the        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      IRB-approved re-disclosure flow                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - If non-material amendment: continue on the original  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      snapshot with stamped version-history                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Required first-turn disclosures per IRB]               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Assistant is a chat tool, not a person               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Assistant is not the research coordinator            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Assistant cannot enroll the patient                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Assistant is providing trial information and         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conducting a preliminary screen                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient can stop at any time                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient can ask to speak to a coordinator at any     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      point                                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Data-retention notice per institutional policy       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: loaded trial context with versioned snapshot;  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    required disclosures delivered]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      312[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
