[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      314[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── TOOL-USE LOOP + IRB-CITATION DISCIPLINE ───────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      316[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [LLM-orchestrated conversation with tool use]           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      317[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - System prompt parameterized per trial, per           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      318[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      population posture, per language                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      319[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - User message plus recent-conversation context        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      320[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool surface:                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      321[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - trial_context_retrieve (IRB-approved corpus only)  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      322[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - recruitment_faq_retrieve (IRB-approved FAQ only)   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      323[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - eligibility_criterion_evaluate (deterministic)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      324[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - trial_state_check                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      325[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - prescreen_capture                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      326[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - coordinator_handoff_schedule                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      327[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - representativeness_record                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      328[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - emergency_route                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      329[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - out_of_scope_route                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      330[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - provenance_retrieve                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      331[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      332[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [IRB-citation discipline]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      333[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every trial-specific assertion must cite an          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      334[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      IRB-approved source document                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      335[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - If the question falls outside the IRB-approved FAQ,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      336[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      route the question to the coordinator rather than    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      337[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      improvising                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      338[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - The LLM produces tool calls, not novel trial         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      339[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      language                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      340[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Citation coverage floor enforced (configurable,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      341[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      typically 85% or higher)                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      342[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      343[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      344[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: composed response with citations and           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      345[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    tool-call audit trail]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      346[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      347[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      348[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      349[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CONVERSATIONAL ELIGIBILITY PRESCREEN ──────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      350[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      351[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Deterministic per-criterion evaluation engine]         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      352[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Simple structured criteria (age, sex, geography,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      353[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      basic diagnosis): evaluated from conversation        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      354[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Complex structured criteria (lab values, medication  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      355[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      history, imaging findings): captured as patient-     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      356[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reported with explicit coordinator-verification      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      357[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      caveat                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      358[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Clinical-judgment criteria (severity, prognosis):    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      359[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      flagged for coordinator review, patient report       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      360[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      captured as input not determination                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      361[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Verification-only criteria: captured, deferred to    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      362[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordinator for source verification                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      363[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      364[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Per-criterion rule ownership]                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      365[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Each criterion has named clinical-leadership         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      366[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      ownership, version history, and IRB-review evidence  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      367[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - The LLM does not interpret eligibility criteria;     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      368[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      it surfaces questions, captures responses, and       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      369[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      routes responses to the deterministic rule engine    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      370[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      371[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Disposition determination]                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      372[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Clearly disqualified (hard exclusion met)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      373[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Uncertain pending coordinator verification           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      374[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Likely eligible pending coordinator confirmation     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      375[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Declined by patient                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      376[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Trial closed or paused (discovered mid-conversation) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      377[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      378[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      379[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: structured prescreen result with per-          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      380[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    criterion evaluation, patient-reported data tagged,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      381[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    clinical-judgment items flagged]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      382[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      383[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      384[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      385[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── OUTPUT SAFETY + IRB-FAITHFULNESS VERIFY ───────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      386[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      387[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard output safety primitives from recipe 11.1]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      388[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scope filter (no recommendation, no diagnosis,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      389[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      no trial comparison)                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      390[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Vendor-managed guardrail layer                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      391[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Persona-and-tone check                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      392[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      393[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Recruitment-specific verification]                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      394[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - IRB-language faithfulness: every trial-specific      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      395[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      statement verified against IRB-approved corpus       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      396[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - No unsupported trial-specific assertions             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      397[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recommendation-language filter (blocks "you should   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      398[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      join", "this trial is right for you", trial          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      399[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      comparison across multiple trials)                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      400[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Distinction between "interest captured" (allowed;    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      401[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      non-consent) and "consent collected" (not allowed;   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      402[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordinator-only) enforced at the output layer       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      403[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - IRB-approved disclosure copy is authored separately  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      404[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and reviewed by the IRB, not generated by the LLM;  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      405[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the disclosure surface is treated as IRB-approved    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      406[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      content, not as LLM-generated text                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      407[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      408[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      409[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: response cleared for delivery, replaced with   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      410[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    a safer template, or regenerated with corrections]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      411[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      412[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      413[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      414[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── COORDINATOR HANDOFF + THROUGHPUT CONTROL ──────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      415[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      416[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Qualified-handoff orchestration]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      417[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Capture patient's preferred follow-up channel and    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      418[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      time                                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      419[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generate structured prescreen summary for            │
